projects.title: Obscure CTF
projects.bodyText:
- A Capture the Flag style vulnerable machine.
 -  Involves a Web CVE in Odoo, docker escape and ret2libc attack.
 - Published on TryHackMe.
 - Multiple writeups/walkthroughs.

projects.title: PyPwnCollege
projects.bodyText:
- A Python library and CLI(command line interface)
 - Used to interact with pwncollege and also to automate.
 - Published on pypi.
 -  Open Source at Github

projects.title: RevWorks
projects.bodyText:
- Ruby on Rails Web Application with some basic functionality.
 - Has a Web Race condition and used in a CTF I hosted. 
 - Has Docker image and live heroku demo.

projects.title: RustC2
projects.bodyText:
- Proof of Concept Command and Control Framework written in Rust
 - Has basic features such as reverse shell handling and management, file upload/download, portscan. 
 - Open Source at Github

projects.title: Twitter-Clone
projects.bodyText:
- Simple Twitter clone with only posts/profile/like/reply functionality.
 - Google oauth2 is setup allowing direct sign-in using google account
- MongoDB database is used along with S3 bucket for images.
 - Open Source at Github

projects.title: Event-Dashboard
projects.bodyText:
- Event Dashboard for finding events
 - Fully interactive with event modal, category popper, event list expansion/collapse.
- Built with typescript, tailwind and redux.
 - Open Source at Github
